"msg":"我係一路親生仔轉去one ui先發覺咁多方便野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"用緊s21,當初唔揀pixel既其中一個原因就係google個ui實在太醜，成個系統操作邏輯又冇三星咁好，完全冇興趣用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"One UI 確係好多嘢畀你set嘅。但係用左幾日既經驗係用佢既選項不斷turn off 佢既功能。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"有得揀你先係老闆<br />\n唔岩用大不了咪off <br />\n慢慢摸熟 其實套ui操作幾有效率<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0RzAq1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0RzAq1.gif&h=46d32398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[quote]<span class=\"x-large\">完善的系統體驗 X 120hz絕頂的流暢度=三星旗艦<br />\n<br />\nOne Ui 可能係全世界最好用既系統</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>系統級操作方式文件檔案分享</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔洗係正你隔離，可以一次過比幾個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7NT7QT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7NT7QT.jpg&h=959aa49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/my9DqSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmy9DqSQ.jpg&h=77313b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相簿太多？<br />\n<br />\n為您的相簿分組  <br />\n將一個相簿拖入另一個相簿以將其合併為一個群組。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpbL8rV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpbL8rV.gif&h=0b334685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擷取長截圖<br />\n擷取螢幕截圖後，輕觸 [捲動擷取] 按鍵以向下捲動螢幕並擷取更多。您甚至可以輕觸並按住 [捲動擷取] 按鍵以在一個長螢幕截圖中擷取整個螢幕或網頁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK8yxTV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK8yxTV.gif&h=eacd791e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手勢操作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/091314_c96a00e85a9ec579b0ae284c6e606fef.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F091314_c96a00e85a9ec579b0ae284c6e606fef.gif&h=7e58f7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一鍵隱藏手勢白條 全螢幕體驗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5S7kNnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5S7kNnE.jpg&h=a860aae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滑動以復原或重做  <br />\n透過以兩指在鍵盤上向左滑動來復原您上次的編輯。以兩指向右滑動以重做編輯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3cO6d5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3cO6d5.gif&h=3d92792a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n控制游標  <br />\n輕觸並按住空格鍵，然後向上或向下拖曳以控制游標。您還可使用多點觸控選擇文字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdpW80R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdpW80R.gif&h=9e95d4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪貼板<br />\n不需再切換，一次過複製及貼上文字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gi5hfeE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGi5hfeE.jpg&h=35417363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文字不能複製？ 文字提取功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCYCfiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCYCfiu.jpg&h=e086a798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung Keyboard 常用字功能<br />\nx 指紋登入帳戶<br />\n<br />\n常用字功能，自動排常用字上頭位，打字更方便快捷，整合Samsung Pass 記密碼儲存後下次直接用指紋登入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LVjMUWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLVjMUWq.jpg&h=61d01a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qhp5q3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhp5q3Y.jpg&h=82630bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想輕鬆GIF分享影片內容？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nx3YL41.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnx3YL41.gif&h=45a56296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不需再不停截圖了，側拉一拍即錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqLn4BS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqLn4BS.jpg&h=ef15982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaQWpBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaQWpBT.jpg&h=854a4a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截圖不只是圖片。<br />\n當你在網頁上截圖時還會同時保留網址，方便瀏覽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DOKpAX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DOKpAX.gif&h=4a25b9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBixby Routines<br />\n<br />\n建立於特定條件下，讓手機自動運行各種設定或操作<br />\n如：當開啟相冊與Youtube時<br />\n則：開啟螢幕自動旋轉<br />\n<br />\n如：連接指定wifi<br />\n則：手機保持解鎖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRAFNsg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRAFNsg.gif&h=c683fe0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">所有Chrome嘅食電問題<br />\n一律建議裝Samsung browser<br />\n對比chrome係慳成倍電&amp;nbsp;<br />\n而且仲有amoled black mode + adblock + One UI單手邏輯 加成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6xnHXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6xnHXn.png&h=bd53ffd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zQEeuVrUptU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzQEeuVrUptU&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=c90adf35\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zQEeuVrUptU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n </blockquote>"},{"pid":"b02d2132dc88996d1262dee2560bb85df0500f6b","tid":2446580,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>- 相機可以直接scan qr code 本來好好，但佢唔顯示URL, 只顯示page 名，咁會係保安漏洞。（iOS 都有呢個問題）<span class=\"red\">pixel 無問題係因為跟本無呢個功能。</span></blockquote><br />\n點會冇啊gcam 不嬲有google lens㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://ibb.co/mtdLYfs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FmtdLYfs&h=427be587&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c9abf4c59f0e82c48fe2944bc44946e6fb71659","tid":2446580,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b02d2132dc88996d1262dee2560bb85df0500f6b","tid":2446580,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>- 相機可以直接scan qr code 本來好好，但佢唔顯示URL, 只顯示page 名，咁會係保安漏洞。（iOS 都有呢